<H4>   Delegation Greeted at Airport </H4>
<F P=102> SK2103153794 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1507 GMT 21 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2103153794 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, March 21 (KCNA) -- A high-level 
delegation of the Defence Ministry of the Kingdom of Cambodia 
led by Co-ministers of Defence Tie Banh and Tie Chamrat arrived 
here today. 
  It was met at the airport by Minister of People's Armed 
Forces O Chin-u and generals and officers of the People's Army. 
  Cambodian Ambassador to Korea Oum Mannorine was also present 
at the airport. 
  A welcome function took place at the airport. 

</TEXT>

