<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   `Might' of Korean-Style Socialism Highlighted </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK2003090794 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0838 GMT 20 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2003090794 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> ["Might of Korean-style Socialism Rooted Among the Masses" </F>
-- KCNA headline] 
  [Text] Pyongyang, March 20 (KCNA) -- The Korean people's 
faith in socialism is an unshakable and unbreakable one and will 
be everlasting, being successfully carried forward through 
generations, stresses NODONG SINMUN in a signed article today. 
  The article says: 
  Now the Korean-style socialism is making a long drive, not 
wavering in any howling wind, because the steadfast faith in 
socialism of chuche which is advancing confidently under the 
guidance of the party and the leader has struck its roots deep 
in the hearts of our people. 
  The Korean people accept the socialist idea of chuche as 
their faith and are making the revolution and construction as 
demanded by it. And they are struggling with a great pride and 
honor of living and making the revolution in the most 
advantageous socialist society in the world. 
  They are firmly convinced through the course of giving full 
play to the dignity and might of the Korean-style socialism 
under the banner of the socialist idea of chuche that they can 
accomplish the cause of socialism when they take as the 
guideline of their struggle the socialist idea of chuche which 
is being developed and completed by the dear leader Comrade Kim 
Chong-il. 
  This faith of our people is immutable and strongest even 
under the circumstances in which the imperialists are 
intensifying anti-socialist moves, loudly advertising "material 
prosperity" and "advantages" of capitalism. 
  The whole society forms one big family and an independent 
and 
creative, socialist life of the people is in full bloom, with 
the entire people united behind the dear leader Comrade Kim 
Chong-il in one mind. Our people deeply bear in mind through 
the present-day reality and the miserable situation in the 
countries where socialism has suffered a setback that capitalism 
has nothing to present to the people. Hence, our people's faith 
in socialism cannot be shaken with anything. 
  The Korean people wholly integrate socialism with their 
destiny and devote their all to the struggle to defend socialism. 

</TEXT>

