<H3> <TI>   SRV Minister, Delegation Depart 21 Mar </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK2103155694 Rangoon Radio Burma in Burmese 1330 GMT 21 Mar 
94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2103155694 </F>
<F P=104>  Rangoon Radio Burma </F>


<TEXT>
