<DOCNO> FBIS3-6796 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreas055_d_94010" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-EAS-94-055 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  22 Mar 1994 </DATE1>

