  [Text] Hanoi VNA March 21 -- Prime Minister Vo Van Kiet 
received here this afternoon Cuban Foreign Minister [F.M.] 
Roberto Robaina Gonzales who is on an official visit to Vietnam. 
  Also present at the reception were Foreign Minister Nguyen 
Manh Cam and Cuban Ambassador to Vietnam Mrs. Tania Maceira 
Delgado. 
  Prime Minister Vo Van Kiet expressed his pleasure at the 
