of the party, government and people of Vietnam towards the 
party, government and people of Cuba in their great efforts to 
overcome present difficulties in order to successfully build and 
defend their countries. 
  On behalf of the party, government and people of Cuba, 
Minister Gonzales expressed his sincere thanks to the party, 
government and people of Vietnam for their valuable support and 
solidarity to Cuba which he considered a great encouragement to 
the Cuban people. 
  Also on hand, at the talks were Deputy Foreign Minister Le 
Mai and Cuban Ambassador to Vietnam Mrs. Tania Maceira Delgado. 

