Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Tokyo, March 22 KYODO -- The Japanese Government 
decided Tuesday [22 March] to donate 750,000 dollars of 
emergency aid to the United Nations Children's Fund (UNICEF) to 
assist millions of Angolans caught in the crossfire of internal 
conflicts, government officials said. The Japanese aid is 
