delivered 
an opening address. The (?five) delegates of nationalities 
group read out proposal papers under the headings of state 
structure and the head of state. Proposal papers were read out 
by five delegates of nationalities group from states and 
divisions. 
  The plenary session recessed as arranged at 1100. The 
afternoon session of the National Convention plenary session is 
continuing at President Residence compound on Ahlone Road. 

