<H3> <TI>   Kim Chong-il Hinted in Charge of Nuclear Issue </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK2303071594 Seoul KBS-1 Radio Network in Korean 0635 GMT 23 
Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK2303071594 </F>
<F P=104>  Seoul KBS-1 Radio Network </F>


