<F P=103> SK2303051994 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, March 23 (KCNA) -- An art troupe of China 
arrived here Tuesday to participate in the 12th April Spring 
Friendship Art Festival. 
  It was met at the airport by Kim Chong-ho, vice-minister of 
Culture and Art and vice-chairman of the organising committee of 
the festival, Sin An-pang, vice-chairman of the Pyongyang 
Municipal Administrative and Economic Committee, officials 
concerned and artistes in the city. 

