<H4>   Kim Il-song Meets Ministers </H4>
<F P=102> SK2403111294 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1031 GMT 24 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2403111294 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, March 24 (KCNA) -- The great leader 
President Kim Il-song today received the high-level delegation 
of the Defence Ministry of the Royal Government of Cambodia 
headed by Co-Ministers of Defence General Tie Banh and General 
Tie Chamrat on a visit to Korea. 
  On hand were Minister of People's Armed Forces O Chin-u and 
Cambodian Ambassador E.P. [extraordinary and plenipotentiary] to 
Korea Oum Mannorine. 
  President Kim Il-song had a talk with the guests in a 
cordial 
and friendly atmosphere. 

